        = (quotient V c).map (f ‚â´ (g‚ÇÅ + g‚ÇÇ)) : by rw (quotient V c).map_comp
    ... = (quotient V c).map (f ‚â´ g‚ÇÅ + f ‚â´ g‚ÇÇ) : by rw preadditive.comp_add
    ... = (quotient V c).map (f ‚â´ g‚ÇÅ) + (quotient V c).map (f ‚â´ g‚ÇÇ) :
